yn rollageagh yn Unnaneys Rollageagh Eddyrashoonagh IAU Ta kuse veg dy cholughtyn preevaadjagh cur enmyssyn rollage er creck ventyr ter enney ec y Lioarlann Ghoaldagh myr ventyr traaghtee neuoarderit Ansherbee tan IAU cur fodjeeaght eddyr eshyn as ny colughtyn shen as cha nel eh jannoo ymmyd jeh ny henmyssyn shen as cha nel ad er enney oc Ga dy vel unnidyn SI as CGS ymmydit dy chur sheese er ardhowshanyn rollageagh ta unnidyn greiney ymmydit dan chooid smoo son dy chur sheese er cruinnaghey soil

ass hiddragien son y chooid smoo agh lesh beggan dy hailium as bunstooghyn elley Chouds ta cree yn rollage gloo dy fondagh ta cooid jehn hiddragien ceaghlit gyn stad gys hailium liorish yn obbraghey ta enmyssit cohaaghey çheshveanagh Tan chooid faagit jeh çheu sthie yn rollage gymmyrkey yn vree magh ass y chree trooid cochiangle dy obbraghyn goulragh as coymmyrkagh Ta broo sthie jehn rollage cur lhiettrimys er tooilley cohuittym fo trimmid yn ymhayrn eck Chouds tan conney hiddragien sy chree er

elg tan ghaa oardagh ryakin Myr sampleyr lioarhasht tasht jeh lioaryn agh tashtfockle tasht jeh focklyn Kiare troyn scanshoil y reiltagh =Imraaghyn= Çheeroaylleeaght She studeyrys er y teihll as ny çheeraghyn troyn cummaltee as obbraghyn eck ee çheeroaylleeaght Ta daa vanglane mooar ec çheeroaylleeaght çheeroaylleeaght deiney as çheeroaylleeaght fishigagh Cha nel ee y red cheddin as kaartgraafeeaght Ga dy row fys er kaartgraafeeaght ec çheeroayllee dy cadjin cha nee shen yn ardobbyr oc Ta çheero

yei ny Nheeghyn Shinney Ec y traa cheddin ta injillaghey schlei ryakin syn ellyn rish ny eashyn chouds ta ny Shoggothyn çheet dy ve ny seyrey as teh ny sdoillee freayll laue yn eaghtyr orroo Ta ny caslyssyn çheet dy ve neureilt as bunneydagh as tad çheet er olk gyn enney ayns sleityn eer ny smoo faggys daue ta cur aggle eer orroosyn Fyyerrey rish y rio snaue roo daag ny Nheeghyn Shinney dys faarkey mooar fohalloo Teh jeeaghyn dy nee fir foddey caillt hooar ny deiney syn ooig as ad ass y çheshagh
yn ellan soit sy valley Rere leigh teh ny chiare valley smoo ny yei Doolish Kione Droghad as Rhumsaa lesh dy chummaltee ayn Cha row Purt ny hInshey ny hardvalley er yn ellan agh she ardagglish Phurt ny hInshey soiaghey Aspick Sodor as Mannin Tee ny purt eeastee smoo scanshoil er yn ellan myrgeddin Tan thie tashtee Thie Vanannan as Thie Tashtee Ymmyrkey Vannin soit ec y phurt Erskyn shen ta Cashtal Phurt ny hInshey soit er yn ellan beg Ellan Noo Perick ta kianglt lesh y vooarheear lesh taagher Sy
NUTS cur Gibraaltar çheumooie jehn UO myr EO as ta Geeaaney ayn daa cheayrt myr FR ny Frank as myr AS ayns America Yiass Ta tree keimyn NUTS er veenaghey as daa cheim unnid reiragh ynnydagh LAU foue Derrey Jerrey Souree she keimyn NUTS as vayn agh hie ad er scryssey dy oikoil Cha nel dagh keim breeoil ec dagh çheer rere y vooadys jee Myr sampleyr ta keimyn NUTS Lucsemburg çheet er y lane heer cha nel agh LAUyn breeoil eck Ta ardjyn NUTS rere aarheynnyn reiragh tayn foast Ayns çheeraghyn gyn agh 
 aawoalley allerjagh myr shen gow kiarail rish bentyn ree Ta fraue mooar eck wheesh as cm fo hallooin Ta fraue rostit cleaysh voddee ynee Vad cliaghtey creck eh myr Portland sago ayns ynnyd stark Injynagh flooyr ny salep Foddee eh ve nieunagh mannagh vel eh jeant dy kiart Tee goll er troarey myr lus jesheenagh Simferopol She caayr er liehinnys y Chrimeea eh Simferopol y mosk bane Myr preeuvalley yn liehinnys she cree politickagh tarmaynagh as arraghey Simferopol Sy vlein va dooinney cummal ayn S
Cabbyl Przewalski currit orroo Ta ny cabbil shen nyn gabbil feie chiart yerrinagh agh ta cabbil feie rygheddyn ayn syn eaynid chammah agh cha nel ayndaue agh cabbil ta jeh sluight thieoilagh John Muir Va John Muir Averil Mee ny Nollick ny najooree screeudeyr as greinneyder son freayltys eaynee ny Steatyn Unnaneysit Screeu eh lettyryn artyn as lioaryn er e chontoyrtyssyn syn aasagh ayns Sierra Nevada er lheh as adsyn er nyn lhiah ec millioonyn dy leih Va laue echey ayns bun y Sierra Club as eshyn
 reeriaght oc fungi She heterotrophyn tayn as boaylley killag chitinagh oc Y chooid smoo jeu ta cummey sniaueyn ylchillagagh orroo ny hyphae as ny sniaueyn shoh jannoo magh mycelium Fir elley tad nyn killagyn nyn lomarcan Dy cadjin ta fungyssyn geddyn sliught liorish sporeyn dy keintyssagh ny dy neucheintyssagh Kuse jeu cha nod geddyn sliught as cha nel adsyn sheelraghey agh liorish gientyn losseragh Ta fungyssyn goaill stiagh jiastyn shalmaneyn as lheeah Ta mooinjerys ny sfaggys eddyr fungi as 
as eh shen çheet magh ass Terra Nova y Ladjyn as ny çhengaghyn gollrhee Tan lught Mikmaq cur Taqamkuk er yn ellan An Leadhb Gharbh She balley beg Gaeltacht er Aran Vooar magh veih coose heear Choontae Ghoon ny Ghoal Nerin ee an Leadhb Gharbh Ta shirveish baatey assaig kiangley yn balley beg rish Ailt an Chorráin er y çheer vooar Ta oik postagh meanscoill purt yn ellan ny lhie sy valley beg Myrane lesh shen ta thie bee shamyr gammanyn as ram thieyn lhionney ayn Ellanyn Vooir Eeaght She ellanragh
